Coffee Date ☕️🫶🏻

A few photos from Ava's solo performances in both Myrtle Beach and last weekend right here in D.C. 🌟 Ava's been looking forward to her @nrgdanceproject competitions for months and they never disappoint! ⚡️⚡️⚡️

“Why" placed 1st overall last weekend in the Teen Division and in the Teen Open category in DC and 4th overall in Myrtle Beach. 

Your dad and I so proud of you, Ava!  @avaa_dougherty You danced beautifully!! ♥️

@buffadance @nrgprodigies #performingarts #dance #lyrical #dancecompetition

I wanted to take a minute celebrate this beautiful girl on her achievements last weekend at In10sity Dance Competiton in Baltimore, MD. 

Ava’s solo, “Why” placed 1st overall in the teen division, she also received 1 of the 3 judges choice awards and an award for “Entertainment”. ⭐️ 

It was such a big weekend for Ava!  She’s been hustling her heart out for months in preparation for this competition season and we love watching her take the stage each weekend and giving it ALL she’s got. 

We’re so, so thankful for the talented choreographers behind Ava’s solos this year that suite her so perfectly.  @mallauri 

So freaking proud of my girl! ♥️

@in10sitydance @buffadance @avaa_dougherty
Celebrating 42 years today with my two favorite girls… 🎈 @avaa_dougherty

Looking back on this beautiful solo for Ava choreographed by @galle_mabalay as we count day the days until @nrgdanceproject Nationals in a few weeks!  @buffadance 🌟 #nrgdanceproject #performingarts #shinebright

Proud of our swimmer today and always! 💦 Hard work in the off-season pays off and she has a new PR in freestyle (22.97 💪🏻) and grabbed 1st place by a sliver of a second in backstroke.  Go, Grace! ❤️ #summerswim
Independence Day with @avaa_dougherty 🇺🇸🌵⭐️

Celebrating Ava and her huge accomplishments competing at NRG Dance Project Nationals this past week! 

YOU DESERVE IT! 

A culmination of years of hard work, dedication, training, sacrifice, passion, and her LOVE for performance and dance all came together on Sunday night establishing a huge milestone for Ava and we couldn’t be happier for our girl. 

Always so impressed with @nrgdanceproject competitions (regional and especially NATIONALS!) whether it be the classes, the teachers and choreographers, and all the fun stuff they mix in between. A huge highlight of Ava's throughout the year!! 

And so grateful for @buffadance and everything they've done for Ava and continue to do for her as she grows as a performer. Such an incredible dance family!! 

The future is so bright, Ava!! 🌟 We are so PROUD OF YOU!!! ❤️

#performingarts #hardwork #determination #dance @nrgdanceproject @nrgprodigies @buffadance

How’d we get so lucky?! Happy 8th birthday, G! 🎉 @avaa_dougherty #summerbaby #eightisgreat #happybirthday
